name: Spring-js
tagline: Javascript agent ideas, tools and love to change the world
body:
### Welcome to Spring-js project.
Spring-js are javascript scripts to connect to Spring framework. The scripts are ready to use. Just down load from [coronadoland / spring-js](https://github.com/coronadoland/spring-js) and use in your code.

### Vision
My experience must be attached the community for reuse by others.

### Mision
Deploy faster and secure the project to invest your in other important things,

### License.
The code is free for any project, but read [License agreement](https://raw.github.com/coronadoland/spring-js/master/LICENSE.txt)


### The last thing to know
Please enjoy.
